result.name: Little Break Coffee & Kitchen

reviews.text: Service is extremely disappointing - for a place with price in its range customers are expected to vacate within 1.5 hours; the rigidity of their requirements means there's no way food could be ordered for sharing, choice on the menu is also rather limited. Oh, and I haven't even mentioned the arrogance of their waiters and the average food quality.

A cafe on the back side of D2 place one. There was a good variety of drink option and the coffee was quite good, fair price. 
The food option was not so much though and only one option of cake was available. The food was ok.
It was quite comfortable to sit in the cafe during afternoon tea time as the staffs were very nice and wouldn't pressure you.
Nice meal in a very chill and comfortable restaurant. One of the best restaurants in Lai Chi Kok. Highly recommended.
The most bitter cappuccino I have ever tasted. It’s more like a restaurant than a cafe for chilling.

We had lunch there on a Sunday afternoon. The place is quite small and the tables quite close to each other so we chose their outdoor table. The food was quite delicious and we love the pork loin the most. But the lunch sets are quite expensive in the range of $150-180.

reviews.text: 不打算再光顧，甜品只有兩個選擇。招呼極差，碟都俾唔夠。最犀利是坐低哂叫左兩個甜品先話最低消費。尚餘半小時都入去，我服左佢地。

Service is extremely disappointing - for a place with price in its range customers are expected to vacate within 1.5 hours; the rigidity of their requirements means there's no way food could be ordered for sharing, choice on the menu is also rather limited. Oh, and I haven't even mentioned the arrogance of their waiters and the average food quality.

A cafe on the back side of D2 place one. There was a good variety of drink option and the coffee was quite good, fair price. 
The food option was not so much though and only one option of cake was available. The food was ok.
It was quite comfortable to sit in the cafe during afternoon tea time as the staffs were very nice and wouldn't pressure you.
第二次光顧，食物賣相一般啦，無特別影低，order左豬扒，蝴蝶粉，的確係好食嘅！咖啡係好飲嘅！係附近做野，可惜lunch menu價錢同dinner 差不多，趕時間的話就真係真心貴了⋯
味道一般，南瓜湯好飲，魚比較梅及鬆散，唔建議食。同事豬，我哋食完飲住餐後茶先有得食，慘慘豬。
